{"tid":2437841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"餐廳食飯應該對坐定平排坐？","createTime":"2021-03-08T06:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T05:43:42.000Z","uid":157831,"like":36,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f3502e0c42cb94453288fa49e69bacb378ff35d2","tid":2437841,"uid":157831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"4人一枱，繁忙時間要搭枱。<br />\n真心唔明點解要侍應要兩個熟人平排坐，食飯抬頭望住對面兩個三唔識七嘅真係好老尷。<br />\n試過有次同公司兩條毒撚去食飯（ok加埋我3個），入到去個侍應帶位坐六人枱，邊鳩知已經有3個金毛mk坐咗一邊，屌佢老母坐到落去唔夠一分鐘卒之頂唔順起身走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟係邊個on9諗要平排坐？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平排坐"},{"pid":"ce27d717601cde41e4a770ab1478b127e886bfb4","tid":2437841,"uid":114814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"睇你點坐先方便你食完走"},{"pid":"333d55c026464928fd2ba5a546ea03b31b7ffe8e","tid":2437841,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"通常係坐係搭枱條友既大髀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9b1ffc3b23e2685b55caed46e47f1d2019402d","tid":2437841,"uid":135114,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"卡位一定係平排坐"},{"pid":"1b6bfaca4887e38f95fda336a9fc2b54a78923d3","tid":2437841,"uid":85205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"認真 搭枱如果卡位要我坐入面，隔離坐個唔識嘅，我會唔想坐，好有壓迫感<br />\n<br />\n平排坐方便出入啊嘛"},{"pid":"a1b417a4eb21733d5abc99c09c418b261cb98b8d","tid":2437841,"uid":157831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1b6bfaca4887e38f95fda336a9fc2b54a78923d3","tid":2437841,"uid":85205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"認真 搭枱如果卡位要我坐入面，隔離坐個唔識嘅，我會唔想坐，好有壓迫感<br />\n<br />\n平排坐方便出入啊嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"咁